---
title: Toasted Brown Rice Bowl with Cashews, Sesame, and Green Beans
description: After-dinner grazers and midnight snackers, take note: this energy bowl is loaded with protein, which means your stomach definitely won’t be grumbling tonight. Plus, it’s got all the Asian-fusion flavors we love: soy, ginger, and garlic.
